<wfdescription>&lt;p&gt;In this single-class activity, an informal debate is held in class around a topic discussed in the course. The purpose of the debate is to help students explore a topic or issue from multiple and angles, and to practice preparing, critically analyzing, and responding to different arguments. See full description here.&lt;/p&gt;</wfdescription>
