<node><name>Prepare Initial Arguments</name>
<id>10</id>
<lefticon>group</lefticon>
<righticon>discuss</righticon>
<column>ICS</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Each side prepares arguments. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Decide who will present, chosen from the students given numbers 1 and 4. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: if other students are really keen to present that's fine. A good rule of thumb is to tell them that they can't have the same person as the main presenter more than once.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: This can be done in either smaller groups, or one large group, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
<linkedwf>undefined</linkedwf>
<textheight>140.80001831054688</textheight>
