<column>ICS</column>
<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Prepare any final arguments&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Finish up with what they feel are still the 1-2 best arguments.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
